#. <section class="sutta" id="an5.49"><article><div class="hgroup"><p class="division">
msgctxt "an5.49:0.1"
msgid "Aṅguttara Nikāya 5"
msgstr "Numbered Discourses 5"

#. </p><p>
msgctxt "an5.49:0.2"
msgid "5. Muṇḍarājavagga"
msgstr "5. With King Muṇḍa"

#. </p><h1>
msgctxt "an5.49:0.3"
msgid "49. Kosalasutta"
msgstr "49. The King of Kosala"

#. </h1></div><p>
#. <a class="pts-vp-pli" id="pts-vp-pli3.57"></a>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc1"></a>
msgctxt "an5.49:1.1"
msgid ""
"Ekaṃ samayaṃ bhagavā sāvatthiyaṃ viharati jetavane anāthapiṇḍikassa ārāme."
msgstr ""
"At one time the Buddha was staying near Sāvatthī in Jeta’s Grove, "
"Anāthapiṇḍika’s monastery."

msgctxt "an5.49:1.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho rājā pasenadi kosalo yena bhagavā tenupasaṅkami; upasaṅkamitvā "
"bhagavantaṃ abhivādetvā ekamantaṃ nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"Then King Pasenadi of Kosala went up to the Buddha, bowed, and sat down to "
"one side."

# See note in text. This line seems dubious.
#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc2"></a>
#. VAR: Tena kho pana samayena mallikā devī kālaṅkatā hoti → etthantare pāṭho sī potthake
msgctxt "an5.49:2.1"
msgid "Tena kho pana samayena mallikā devī kālaṅkatā hoti."
msgstr ""

msgctxt "an5.49:2.2"
msgid ""
"Atha kho aññataro puriso yena rājā pasenadi kosalo tenupasaṅkami; "
"upasaṅkamitvā rañño pasenadissa kosalassa upakaṇṇake āroceti:"
msgstr "Then a man went up to the king and whispered in his ear:"

#. VAR: mallikā devī, deva → deva devī (s1-3, km, pts1)
msgctxt "an5.49:2.3"
msgid "“mallikā devī, deva, kālaṅkatā”ti."
msgstr "“Your Majesty, Queen Mallikā has passed away.”"

msgctxt "an5.49:2.4"
msgid ""
"Evaṃ vutte, rājā pasenadi kosalo dukkhī dummano pattakkhandho adhomukho "
"pajjhāyanto appaṭibhāno nisīdi."
msgstr ""
"When this was said, King Pasenadi was miserable and sad. He sat with his "
"shoulders drooping, downcast, depressed, with nothing to say."

#. </p><p>
#. <a class="sc" id="sc3"></a>
msgctxt "an5.49:3.1"
msgid ""
"Atha kho bhagavā rājānaṃ pasenadiṃ kosalaṃ dukkhiṃ dummanaṃ pattakkhandhaṃ "
"adhomukhaṃ pajjhāyantaṃ appaṭibhānaṃ viditvā rājānaṃ pasenadiṃ kosalaṃ "
"etadavoca:"
msgstr "Knowing this, the Buddha said to him:"

msgctxt "an5.49:3.2"
msgid ""
"“pañcimāni, mahārāja, alabbhanīyāni ṭhānāni samaṇena vā brāhmaṇena vā devena "
"vā mārena vā brahmunā vā kenaci vā lokasmiṃ."
msgstr ""
"“Great king, there are five things that cannot be had by any ascetic or "
"brahmin or god or Māra or Brahmā or by anyone in the world."

msgctxt "an5.49:3.3"
msgid "Katamāni pañca?"
msgstr "What five?"

msgctxt "an5.49:3.4"
msgid ""
"‘Jarādhammaṃ mā jīrī’ti alabbhanīyaṃ ṭhānaṃ … pe … na socanāya paridevanāya …"
" pe … kammaṃ daḷhaṃ kinti karomi dānī”ti."
msgstr ""
"That someone liable to old age should not grow old. … Sorrowing and "
"lamenting doesn’t do even a little bit of good … ‘The karma is strong. What "
"can I do now?’”"

#. </p><p class="endsection">
msgctxt "an5.49:3.5"
msgid "Navamaṃ."
msgstr ""
